class=\"cl-96ff8250\">9,310,302</span></p></td></tr><tr style=\"overflow-wrap:break-word;\"><td class=\"cl-97068910\"><p class=\"cl-9706625a\"><span class=\"cl-96ff8250\">Burden_25</span></p></td><td class=\"cl-97068911\"><p class=\"cl-9706626e\"><span class=\"cl-96ff8250\">2,327,576</span></p></td></tr><tr style=\"overflow-wrap:break-word;\"><td class=\"cl-97068910\"><p class=\"cl-9706625a\"><span class=\"cl-96ff8250\">Burden_40</span></p></td><td class=\"cl-97068911\"><p class=\"cl-9706626e\"><span class=\"cl-96ff8250\">3,724,121</span></p></td></tr><tr style=\"overflow-wrap:break-word;\"><td class=\"cl-97068910\"><p class=\"cl-9706625a\"><span class=\"cl-96ff8250\">TotalCost_25</span></p></td><td class=\"cl-97068911\"><p class=\"cl-9706626e\"><span class=\"cl-96ff8250\">11,637,878</span></p></td></tr><tr style=\"overflow-wrap:break-word;\"><td class=\"cl-9706891a\"><p class=\"cl-9706625a\"><span class=\"cl-96ff8250\">TotalCost_40</span></p></td><td class=\"cl-9706891b\"><p class=\"cl-9706626e\"><span class=\"cl-96ff8250\">13,034,423</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div>\n```\n\n:::\n:::\n\n\n\nTherefore to raise everyone's pay by 6% the total cost would be between **$11.6M - $13M** \n\n* The cost for 6% raises is $9.3M\n* The additional employeer cost due to payroll taxes / benfits: between $2.3M and $3.7M\n\n",
